  "body": "### Issue\r\nSee https://github.com/cfrg/draft-irtf-cfrg-bls-signature/issues/22\r\n\r\n[The Eth2 spec is using the latest IETF BLS spec (draft **v2**)](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/8e82ca5d1ad6d651ef3410552c4bc13c16325f63/specs/phase0/beacon-chain.md#bls-signatures), which points to IETF hash-to-curve spec draft **v6**. But we need IETF hash-to-curve spec draft **v7**. The status-quo BLS v2 + H2C v7 is an awkward custom version for us. Currently waiting for the IETF BLS working group to cut the next release.\r\n\r\nThere should be **no** substantive change of `BLS_SIG_BLS12381G2_XMD:SHA-256_SSWU_RO_POP_` ciphersuite that Eth2 is using.",
