    "body": "Brief update on this.  The IETF \"draft 2\" for BLS signatures expired yesterday, 10 Sep 2020.  [https://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-irtf-cfrg-bls-signature-02](https://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-irtf-cfrg-bls-signature-02)\r\n\r\nThe site does not seem to yet have the \"draft 3\" posted; but perhaps I'm looking in the wrong place.\r\n\r\nEither way, the Eth2.0 spec doc comment re IETF and draft 2 is now out of date and incorrect.\r\n[eth2.0-specs/...bls-signatures](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/dev/specs/phase0/beacon-chain.md#bls-signatures)",
